snippet.title: Crayta Stadia Connect Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Crayta is a collaborative game creation, sharing, and play platform, coming exclusively to Stadia, Summer 2020. It brings together people of all ages, experience, ability and background to create multiplayer games. All trailer footage was captured within Crayta. www.crayta.com

Stay up to date by following us:
Twitter: https://twitter.com/CraytaGame
Discord: https://discord.gg/crayta
Instagram: https://instagram.com/CraytaGame
Reddit: https://www.reddit.com/r/Crayta
Medium: https://medium.com/crayta
Play now: https://www.crayta.com/

PEGI Rating: 12 (Violence, In-Game Purchases)
ESRB Rating: T (Violence; In-Game Purchases, Users Interact)

#Crayta #Stadia
